This paper discusses the performance evaluation of RDF Stream Processing engines, which involves processing and analyzing large amounts of data in real-time. This topic is closely related to several sub-categories of computer science, including database systems (cs.DB), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), distributed computing (cs.DC), software engineering (cs.SE), and data mining (cs.DL).
